<h5 id="subject_742640">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=36b752c53b0f301795115ca6597f7676&amp;topic=77570.msg742640#msg742640" rel="nofollow">Re: 钢之守护神RPG（メタリックガーディアンRPG）-规则书</a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_742640'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_742640'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #48 于:</strong> 2015-08-09, 周日 03:20:38 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_742640_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
